reports.title: Page Rank vs Number of Views
reports.query:
MATCH (n:Video)
WHERE n.pageRank > 2.5
RETURN n.pageRank as PageRank, 
       n.ratings as ratings,n.views as views,
       n.comments as comments

reports.title: Number of videos in each category
reports.query:
MATCH (v:Video)
RETURN v.category AS Category, COUNT(v) AS VideoCount

reports.title: Number of Views Per Video Category
reports.query:
MATCH (v:Video)
RETURN v.category AS PageRank, v.views as views

reports.title: Number of Relations vs Page Rank
reports.query:
MATCH (n:Video)-[r]-()
WITH n, COUNT(r) AS NumberOfRelations
RETURN NumberOfRelations, n.pageRank AS PageRank LIMIT 3000

reports.title: Total Connections vs Average Page Rank
reports.query:
MATCH (n:Video)
WITH n, 
     COUNT { (n)<--() } AS inDegree, 
     COUNT { (n)-->() } AS outDegree
WITH inDegree, outDegree, (inDegree + outDegree) AS totalDegree, n.pageRank AS pageRank
RETURN totalDegree AS TotalConnections, AVG(pageRank) AS AvgPageRank
ORDER BY TotalConnections
